<subSubSection id="79AA5C93FF83FFC24CC5199B0AD89B26" pageId="6" pageNumber="131" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="310F0F18FF83FFC24CC5199B0AD89B26" blockId="6.[824,1477,1122,1946]" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">
is in fact a species from 
<collectingCountry id="49A74F88FF83FFC24BC9199B0BF59AC6" box="[1177,1256,1730,1754]" name="Angola" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">Angola</collectingCountry>
and it is not known from 
<collectingCountry id="49A74F88FF83FFC24C2319BB0CEE9AE6" box="[883,1011,1762,1786]" name="Cape Verde" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">Cape Verde</collectingCountry>
. The 
<typeStatus id="EE0BB1BAFF83FFC24B7C19BB0B479AE6" box="[1068,1114,1762,1786]" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="F6B0749BFF83FFC24B2F19BB0BC19AE6" box="[1151,1244,1762,1786]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Cyphia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="131" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="stheno">
<emphasis id="03C4D30AFF83FFC24B2F19BB0BC19AE6" box="[1151,1244,1762,1786]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">C. stheno</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was wrongly labelled as from “Cap-vert. Herbier rapporté du 
<collectingCountry id="49A74F88FF83FFC24BB5185B0A5D9B06" box="[1253,1344,1794,1818]" name="Portugal" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">Portugal</collectingCountry>
en 1808 par 
<collectorName id="9C456ACEFF83FFC24C68187B0B359B26" box="[824,1064,1826,1850]" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">
M. 
<location id="346F59C3FF83FFC24C0E187B0CC69B26" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:B919BE0EFF83FFC24C0E19DB0AD89B26:346F59C3FF83FFC24C0E187B0CC69B26" box="[862,987,1826,1850]" country="Cape Verde" municipality="St. Hilaire" name="Geoffroy St." pageId="6" pageNumber="131">
Geoffroy 
<collectingMunicipality id="D16B9562FF83FFC24CEF187B0CC69B26" box="[959,987,1826,1850]" pageId="6" pageNumber="131">St.</collectingMunicipality>
</location>
Hilaire
</collectorName>
”. This is most certainly a Silva collection.
</paragraph>
